(33, 1, '2018-11-20 22:00:45', '2018-11-21 04:00:45', '{\n    \"mesmerize::page_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"{\\\"5\\\":\\\"<div  id=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-color: #ffffff;\\\\\\\" data-label=\\\\\\\"Overlappable\\\\\\\" data-id=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4\\\\\\\" data-export-id=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4\\\\\\\" data-category=\\\\\\\"overlappable\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4 content-section content-section-spacing\\\\\\\" data-overlap=\\\\\\\"true\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"gridContainer\\\\\\\"> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"row spaced-cols text-center\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding col-md-6 \\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-cogs large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\\\\\\\"></i> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">\\u00bfQu\\u00e9 es el club UPIITA-BLOCKCHAIN?</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Es un espacio multi-institucional multi-disciplinario que busca la divulgacion y generacion de tecnologia blockchain&nbsp;</p></div> </div><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding col-md-6 \\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-clone large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\\\\\\\"></i> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">\\u00bfA que nos dedicamos</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Las principales actividades dentro del club son la divulgacion de la tecnologica blockchain y el desarrollar herramientas en base esta tecnologia</p></div> </div>  </div> </div></div><div  id=\\\\\\\"content-13\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-color: #f5fafd;\\\\\\\" data-label=\\\\\\\"Content\\\\\\\" data-id=\\\\\\\"content-2\\\\\\\" data-export-id=\\\\\\\"content-2\\\\\\\" data-category=\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"content-2 content-section content-section-spacing\\\\\\\"><div > <div  class=\\\\\\\"row middle-xs\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-5 bg-image shadow-large-black\\\\\\\" data-bg=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-image: url(&quot;http://localhost/politech/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/cropped-bitcoin-3089728_960_720.jpg&quot;);\\\\\\\"></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-7 full-col-left-padding full-col-right-padding\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"space-bottom-small content-title-col\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Importancia</h5> <h2  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Blockchain</h2> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Hoy en d\\u00eda estamos viviendo una revoluci\\u00f3n encabezada por el denominado  internet del valor que transformar\\u00e1 las industrias bancarias, financieras y junto con el internet de las cosas   se modificara operativamente muchas \\u00e1reas de la industria en general.Debido al potencial tecnol\\u00f3gico de Blockchain en esta revolucion, ignorar esta tecnolog\\u00eda, es un lujo que no podemos darnos, con un amplio espectro de aplicaci\\u00f3n, limitado solo por nuestra capacidad de imaginaci\\u00f3n.&nbsp; El potencial tecnol\\u00f3gico de Blockchain es caracterizado por su capacidad para la:&nbsp;</p></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row spaced-cols \\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Trazabilidad</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Para  cualquier inmueble,  se podr\\u00eda ver quien fue su primer propietario y quienes le siguieron hasta llegar a su \\u00faltimo due\\u00f1o.</p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Seguridad</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Algunos datos que el propietario o el gobierno determine que deban estar ocultos ser\\u00e1n encriptados</p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Transparencia</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Es posible crear navegadores que pueda ser ejecutado desde cualquier parte del mundo  que permitan explorar todo el expediente de un inmueble </p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Inmutabilidad</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"> Una vez que la transacci\\u00f3n ha sido registrada en la cadena de bloques, ser\\u00e1 nada rentable pagar por buscar modificar  de manera ilegal alg\\u00fan atributo de la transacci\\u00f3n</p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Descentralizaci\\u00f3n</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Promueve la no centralizacion de la administraci\\u00f3n lo cual ayuda evitar la corrupci\\u00f3n</p></div></div></div> </div></div> </div><div  id=\\\\\\\"features-3\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-color: #ffffff;\\\\\\\" data-label=\\\\\\\"Features\\\\\\\" data-id=\\\\\\\"features-12-card-bordered\\\\\\\" data-export-id=\\\\\\\"features-12-card-bordered\\\\\\\" data-category=\\\\\\\"features\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"features-12-card-bordered content-section content-section-spacing \\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"gridContainer\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row text-center\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"section-title-col\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h2  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Areas del club</h2> <p  class=\\\\\\\"lead\\\\\\\">Para poder desarrollar las actividades que llevamos acabo en el club hemos decidido dividirlas en subareas, cada una de ella con necesidades especificas, es importante mencionar que no una vez dentro podras incluirte en m\\u00e1s de una area</p></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row spaced-cols\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-connectdevelop round bordered color2\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data