llo de la \\u201cPlataforma para evaluaci\\u00f3n de aprendizajes y registro de calificaciones\\u201d descrito en la secci\\u00f3n de introducci\\u00f3n.<br >\\u2022\\\\tHardware: Se comenzar\\u00e1 con el an\\u00e1lisis, dise\\u00f1o y desarrollo de una Cool Wallet que incorpore alguna caracter\\u00edstica biom\\u00e9trica como la huella dactilar para que sea vinculado con la llave privada de un usuario de Bitcoin.</p><h6 class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\" >Perfil academico o profesional</h6><p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Cualquier ingenieria, empresario o emprendedor</p></div> </div></div> </div><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon color2 fa-angle-double-down bordered round\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"color2\\\\\\\">Ciencias duras</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Encriptaci\\u00f3n, Teor\\u00eda de grafos (Directed Acyclic Graph), funciones hash, entre otros. \\\\n</p><h6  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Perfil academico o profesional\\\\n</h6><p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Matem\\u00e1tico, F\\u00edsico, Actuario</p></div> </div></div> </div><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon color2 fa-battery-half bordered round\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"color2\\\\\\\">Mercadotecnia y Publicidad</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Sera en grupo que desarrolle las siguientes \\u00e1reas:<br >\\u2022\\\\tSitio web<br >\\u2022\\\\tImagen corporativa<br >\\u2022\\\\tRelaciones comerciales y mercadotecnia<br >\\u2022\\\\tRedes sociales</p><h6  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Perfil academico o profesional\\\\n</h6><p  class=\\\\\