(42, 1, '2018-11-20 22:43:01', '2018-11-21 04:43:01', '{\n    \"mesmerize::page_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"{\\\"5\\\":\\\"<div  id=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-color: #ffffff;\\\\\\\" data-label=\\\\\\\"Overlappable\\\\\\\" data-id=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4\\\\\\\" data-export-id=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4\\\\\\\" data-category=\\\\\\\"overlappable\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"overlappable-4 content-section content-section-spacing\\\\\\\" data-overlap=\\\\\\\"true\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"gridContainer\\\\\\\"> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"row spaced-cols text-center\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding col-md-6 \\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-cogs large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\\\\\\\"></i> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">\\u00bfQu\\u00e9 es el club UPIITA-BLOCKCHAIN?</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Es un espacio multi-institucional multi-disciplinario que busca la divulgacion y generacion de tecnologia blockchain&nbsp;</p></div> </div><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding col-md-6 \\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-clone large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\\\\\\\"></i> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">\\u00bfA que nos dedicamos</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Las principales actividades dentro del club son la divulgacion de la tecnologica blockchain y el desarrollar herramientas en base esta tecnologia</p></div> </div>  </div> </div></div><div  id=\\\\\\\"content-13\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-color: #f5fafd;\\\\\\\" data-label=\\\\\\\"Content\\\\\\\" data-id=\\\\\\\"content-2\\\\\\\" data-export-id=\\\\\\\"content-2\\\\\\\" data-category=\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"content-2 content-section content-section-spacing\\\\\\\"><div > <div  class=\\\\\\\"row middle-xs\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-5 bg-image shadow-large-black\\\\\\\" data-bg=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-image: url(&quot;http://localhost/politech/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/cropped-bitcoin-3089728_960_720.jpg&quot;);\\\\\\\"></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-7 full-col-left-padding full-col-right-padding\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"space-bottom-small content-title-col\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Importancia</h5> <h2  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Blockchain</h2> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Hoy en d\\u00eda estamos viviendo una revoluci\\u00f3n encabezada por el denominado  internet del valor que transformar\\u00e1 las industrias bancarias, financieras y junto con el internet de las cosas   se modificara operativamente muchas \\u00e1reas de la industria en general.Debido al potencial tecnol\\u00f3gico de Blockchain en esta revolucion, ignorar esta tecnolog\\u00eda, es un lujo que no podemos darnos, con un amplio espectro de aplicaci\\u00f3n, limitado solo por nuestra capacidad de imaginaci\\u00f3n.&nbsp; El potencial tecnol\\u00f3gico de Blockchain es caracterizado por su capacidad para la:&nbsp;</p></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row spaced-cols \\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Trazabilidad</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Para  cualquier inmueble,  se podr\\u00eda ver quien fue su primer propietario y quienes le siguieron hasta llegar a su \\u00faltimo due\\u00f1o.</p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Seguridad</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Algunos datos que el propietario o el gobierno determine que deban estar ocultos ser\\u00e1n encriptados</p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Transparencia</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Es posible crear navegadores que pueda ser ejecutado desde cualquier parte del mundo  que permitan explorar todo el expediente de un inmueble </p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"><h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Inmutabilidad</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"> Una vez que la transacci\\u00f3n ha sido registrada en la cadena de bloques, ser\\u00e1 nada rentable pagar por buscar modificar  de manera ilegal alg\\u00fan atributo de la transacci\\u00f3n</p></div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs-6\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Descentralizaci\\u00f3n</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Promueve la no centralizacion de la administraci\\u00f3n lo cual ayuda evitar la corrupci\\u00f3n</p></div></div></div> </div></div> </div><div  id=\\\\\\\"about-1\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-color: #f5fafd;\\\\\\\" data-label=\\\\\\\"About\\\\\\\" data-id=\\\\\\\"about-1\\\\\\\" data-export-id=\\\\\\\"about-1\\\\\\\" data-category=\\\\\\\"about\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"about-1 content-section\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"gridContainer\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row text-center\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"section-title-col\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\">  <h2  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Se parte de&nbsp;<span  href=\\\\\\\"#\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"font-weight: 700; font-family: Playfair Display,sans-serif; font-style: italic;\\\\\\\">la revolucion&nbsp; blockchain&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;que esta cambiando al mundo</h2> <p  class=\\\\\\\"lead\\\\\\\">No es necesario que tengas conocmientos previos de como funciona esta tecnologia, lo unico que necesitamos es tu entusiamo y tus ganas de aprender.</p></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"button-holder space-bottom space-bottom-small\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-xs bottom-xs flexbox image-group-bottom-3-img space-bottom-xs center-xs\\\\\\\"> <img  class=\\\\\\\"left-img shadow-large-black\\\\\\\" data-size=\\\\\\\"500x300\\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\\"http://localhost/politech/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/computer-2569652.jpg\\\\\\\"> <img  class=\\\\\\\"center-img shadow-large-black\\\\\\\" data-size=\\\\\\\"500x300\\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\\"http://localhost/politech/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/apple-1838564.jpg\\\\\\\"> <img  class=\\\\\\\"right-img shadow-large-black\\\\\\\" data-size=\\\\\\\"500x300\\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\\"http://localhost/politech/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/laptop-2559795.jpg\\\\\\\"></div> </div></div> </div><div  id=\\\\\\\"features-3\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"background-color: #ffffff;\\\\\\\" data-label=\\\\\\\"Features\\\\\\\" data-id=\\\\\\\"features-12-card-bordered\\\\\\\" data-export-id=\\\\\\\"features-12-card-bordered\\\\\\\" data-category=\\\\\\\"features\\\\\\\" class=\\\\\\\"features-12-card-bordered content-section content-section-spacing \\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"gridContainer\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row text-center\\\\\\\"><div  class=\\\\\\\"section-title-col\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h2  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Areas del club</h2> <p  class=\\\\\\\"lead\\\\\\\">Para poder desarrollar las actividades que llevamos acabo en el club hemos decidido dividirlas en subareas, cada una de ella con necesidades especificas, es importante mencionar que no una vez dentro podras incluirte en m\\u00e1s de una area</p></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row spaced-cols\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-connectdevelop round bordered color2\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"color2\\\\\\\">Estado del arte</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Se har\\u00e1 una investigaci\\u00f3n documental de los proyectos de c\\u00f3digo abierto l\\u00edderes por el desarrollo de su propia tecnolog\\u00eda y por el enfoque de plataforma base para el desarrollo de otras tecnolog\\u00edas. Para comenzar se propone los ICO: Bitcoin, Ethereum, Cardano, Iota y ByteBall; Los protocolos: Lightning network, Segwit\\\\n</p><h6  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Perfil academico o profesional\\\\n</h6><p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Todas las licenciaturas</p></div> </div></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-codepen round bordered color2\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"color2\\\\\\\">Lenguajes</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Formaci\\u00f3n en los lenguajes de programaci\\u00f3n Haskell y Solidity, como principales lenguajes para el establecimiento de Smartcontract.</p><h6  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Perfil academico o profesional</h6><p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Informatica, Computacion, etc.</p></div> </div></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-cube round bordered color2\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"color2\\\\\\\">Aplicaci\\u00f3n pr\\u00e1ctica</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Se trabajara en tres etapas: <br >\\u2022\\\\tClonaci\\u00f3n: Se reproduce toda una plataforma tecnol\\u00f3gica en su mainNet, nodos, wallets y exploradores para analizar y estudiar sus componentes. <br >\\u2022\\\\tExperimentaci\\u00f3n: Se busca crear ambientes de aplicaci\\u00f3n pr\\u00e1ctica para evaluar aspectos como: aceptaci\\u00f3n del usuario, tiempos de respuesta de la operaci\\u00f3n, confiabilidad, fortaleza contra ataques de hackers, etc.<br >\\u2022\\\\tDesarrollo tecnol\\u00f3gico: Se busca dise\\u00f1ar nuevos enfoques de soluci\\u00f3n que sean m\\u00e1s eficientes o que se apliquen a contextos diferentes a los que fueron creados.<br >.</p><h6  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Perfil academico o profesional</h6><p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Informatica o computaci\\u00f3n</p></div> </div></div> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon fa-database round bordered color2\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"color2\\\\\\\">Ingenier\\u00eda</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Se trabajara en las siguientes \\u00e1reas de desarrollo:<br >\\u2022\\\\tSoftware: Se har\\u00e1 el an\\u00e1lisis, dise\\u00f1o y desarrollo de la \\u201cPlataforma para evaluaci\\u00f3n de aprendizajes y registro de calificaciones\\u201d descrito en la secci\\u00f3n de introducci\\u00f3n.<br >\\u2022\\\\tHardware: Se comenzar\\u00e1 con el an\\u00e1lisis, dise\\u00f1o y desarrollo de una Cool Wallet que incorpore alguna caracter\\u00edstica biom\\u00e9trica como la huella dactilar para que sea vinculado con la llave privada de un usuario de Bitcoin.</p><h6  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Perfil academico o profesional</h6><p  class=\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\">Cualquier ingenieria, empresario o emprendedor</p></div> </div></div> </div><div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-6\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"card row-card bordered y-move\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\"> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm-fit icon-column\\\\\\\"> <i  class=\\\\\\\"fa icon color2 fa-angle-double-down bordered round\\\\\\\"></i> </div> <div  class=\\\\\\\"col-sm\\\\\\\" data-type=\\\\\\\"column\\\\\\\"> <h5  class=\\\\\\\"color2\\\\\\\">Ciencias duras</h5> <p  class=\\\\\\\"\\